                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4694" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0377</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10225 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药“花儿朵朵”培训体系的迭代之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The iterative road of &quot;Blossoming Flowers&quot; training system in Yunnan Baiyao</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄波，王延玲，谢立新，江新会，顾江洪，艾谱明，黄丽丽，杨会</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">花儿朵朵培训体系；培训需求；内训师选拔；三七花后备人才开发；2020百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Blossoming Flowers” training system; Training demand analysis; Internal trainer selection; Development of reserve talents</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药是云南企业中的标杆，自2011年开始酝酿、建立和完善分层级的“花儿朵朵”系列干部员工培训体系。本案例着重描述了中药资源事业部新业务培训过程中的培训需求分析和内训师选拔过程中遇到的问题，以及“三七花后备人才开发培养计划”中的困境和出路。案例通过结合公司培训主管梅经理的困惑以及部分受训人员的切身感受展开，介绍了公司的发展背景以及培训体系的由来、发展中碰到的问题、改进历程和取得的成效。案例以真实事件为背景，期望读者能从中提炼出企业如何进行培训需求分析、选拔适合的内训师及后备人才开发有效性的一般规律，同时案例中还抛出了一些决策性问题，望读者能基于培训开发的理论和实践思考相应对策，进而达到提高案例学习水平的目的。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As one of the most successful benchmarking enterprises in Yunnan Province, Yunnan Baiyao has established a series of star employees’ training system named as &quot;Blossoming Flowers&quot; since 2011. This case discusses the problems encountered in the process of training demand analysis and internal trainers selection during the new business training periods in traditional Chinese Medicine Resources Business Department, as well as the difficulties and solutions in the development of the training plan of the reserve talents indicated by Panax notoginseng in the headquarter. Specifically, the case first introduces the development background of the company, and the origin of the training system. Then, motivating by the confusion of Manager Mei, the training director of the company, and the personal feelings of some trainees, the case introduces the problems encountered in the development process of the training system, the improvement process of the system and the benefits the system has brought. On the basis of the analysis of real events, the readers are expected to extract the general rules of how to analyze the training demands of enterprises and how to select suitable internal trainers and reserve talents for development effectiveness. At the same time, some decision-making problems are also raised in the case, and the readers are suggested to consider the corresponding countermeasures based on the theory and practice of training, so as to improve the effectiveness of studying the case.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《战略人力资源管理》、《培训与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">培训开发管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
